 <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.524</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:62\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.62</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg004.perseus-grc1:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OT\">OT</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg004.perseus-grc1:95\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">95</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:125\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.125</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"d\" id=\"n3398.3\" level=\"4\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> less freq. c. dupl. gen. pers. et rei, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">hear of</tr_> a thing <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">from</tr_> a person, as <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:17:115\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.115</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg018.perseus-grc1:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.9</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"e\" id=\"n3398.4\" level=\"4\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> with <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ part.\">part.</a></mood> or <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood> added, as <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἰ πτώσσοντας ὑφ᾽ Ἕκτορι π